Class ParametrizedGETOutput

java.lang.Object
InfrastructureManager.PlatformObject
InfrastructureManager.Modules.REST.RESTModuleObject
InfrastructureManager.Modules.REST.Output.GETOutput
InfrastructureManager.Modules.REST.Output.ParametrizedGETOutput
All Implemented Interfaces:
PlatformOutput
public class ParametrizedGETOutput
extends GETOutput
Subclass of GETOutput that represent outputs that handle resource creation when the defined URL has path parameters included. This means, the resource created is to be binded with a specific parameter (e.g. "id").
